= Description

The application is an interactive tutorial, allowing users to use a REPL to
follow along the teaching material

= Topics covered

- Creating WPF UI using XAML
- Creating domain-specific-languages (DSLs) in Ruby
- Using the Unit::Test testing framework

= Running the app

cd Samples\Tutorial
ir.exe wpf_tutorial.rb

= Running the tests

cd Samples\Tutorial
ir.exe test\test_console.rb

